Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.generic

Contains replacement command, response, command extension and response extension classes for the Key-Value Mapping and Registrant Transfer generic extensions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DomainInfoKVResponseExtension
    Extension of the domain mapping of the EPP info response, as defined in RFC5730 and RFC5731, to generic domain names, the specification of which is in the XML schema definition urn:X-ar:params:xml:ns:kv-1.0.
    DomainKVCommandExtension
    This class models the command elements as specified in the XML schema definition urn:X-ar:params:xml:ns:kv-1.0.
    DomainRegistrantTransferCommand
    In cases where the legal registrant of a domain name has changed, this class should be used to request a transfer of registrant.
    DomainRegistrantTransferCommandType
    The base class for the Domain Registrant Transfer Command.
    DomainRegistrantTransferResponse
    Use this to access registrant transfer data for a domain as provided in an EPP registrantTransfer response using the urn:X-ar:params:xml:ns:registrant-1.0 namespace.

Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.generic Description

Contains replacement command, response, command extension and response extension classes for the Key-Value Mapping and Registrant Transfer generic extensions.
